{{Quote|I wish we had furry creatures like you where I came from.|Cindel|<ref name="Caravan">''[[Caravan of Courage: An Ewok Adventure]]''</ref>}}
The '''Towani family'''<ref name="Name">''[[The Essential Guide to Characters]]''</ref> was a family of [[Human/Legends|Humans]] who crash-landed on [[Endor/Legends|Endor]] in approximately [[3 ABY/Legends|3 ABY]] during the [[Imperial Era/Legends|Imperial Era]]. During the stay the parents were kidnapped by the [[Gorax/Legends|Gorax]], and the kids, with the help of the [[Ewok/Legends|Ewoks]], managed to free them. When nearly ready to leave, a group of [[Sanyassan/Legends|Sanyassan]] Marauders [[Raid on Bright Tree Village|attacked]] [[Bright Tree Village/Legends|Bright Tree Village]], killing many and capturing the rest. Of the Towanis, only Cindel survived.

