==Behind the scenes==
The [[Star Wars Legends|Legends]] timeline places the two Ewok films prior to the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]], but ''Caravan of Courage'' producer [[Thomas G. Smith|Tom Smith]] says this was not necessarily the original intent.<ref name="bt25">[[Bantha Tracks 25|''Bantha Tracks'' 25]]</ref> Placing the Ewok films after [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Return of the Jedi'']] does explain why [[Wicket Wystri Warrick/Legends|Wicket Wystri Warrick]], who by [[Ewoks: The Battle for Endor|''The Battle for Endor'']] had developed a working vocabulary in [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], did not understand [[Princess/Legends|Princess]] [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia]].

